  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Calling upon fell powers, a witch can place a hex on a creature within 60 feet that causes its sleep to be tormented by terrible nightmares. This functions as the spell @Compendium[pf1.spells.siv3ub7hbmcklf8c]{Nightmare} each time the affected creature attempts to rest. A Will save negates this effect. If the save is failed, the target must make a new save each night or be unable to rest.</p>"
